    <div class="lg:w-[300px] text-center lg:text-start">
        <p class="pb-[30px]">
            “Because the people who are crazy enough
            to think they can change the world, are the ones who do.”
        </p>
        <p>
            - Steve Jobs
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full lg:w-[740px] mx-auto xl:grid md:grid-cols-4 md:gap-6 items-center 
                flex justify-center [&>a]:px-2 [&>a]:pt-10">
        <a href="https://github.com/JoeSs27">
            <GithubIcon class="size-[50px] hover:scale-150 transition" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/joe-salazar">
